TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message:
Some arm units landed scattered across a tropical achepelago, in the midst of a battle between two rival core factions. The two core factions will initially be preoccupied fighting each other and you should be able to mine plenty of metal from the central islands before they notice you. We hope it will be safe for you to make a base in the east of the southern island.
Establish our camp and await further orders.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: Units are massing on either side and it looks like the next battle will be on the central islands. It might help to retreat back to the southern island, but don't miss out on reclaiming the wrecks left over from sea battles.

Our intelligence suggests the core in the north island are destroying the revolution in the south using flying fortresses. You'd better get ready - after crushing the revolution they are likely to come for you. Destroy the three enemy aircraft plants on the north island to complete the mission.
